OL,6,FFire crews on are appealing to the
OL,7,Fpublic for help after one of their
OL,8,Fengines was attacked.
OL,10,Fsaid the vehicle was targeted by young
OL,11,Fpeople on a number of occasions while
OL,12,Fattending callouts in the Grangetown
OL,13,Farea of across the weekend.
OL,15,FOne attack, which happened in
OL,16,FBirchington Avenue after midnight on
OL,17,FMonday 13 May, saw the windscreen
OL,18,Fseverely damaged by bricks, meaning
OL,19,Fthe engine will be off the road until
OL,20,Fit can be repaired.
