OL,7,Ffinancial cost, it means one less fire
OL,8,Fengine is available to attend a real-
OL,9,Flife emergency callouts.
OL,11,FSimon Weastell, assistant chief fire
OL,12,Fofficer, said: "It is completely
OL,13,Funacceptable for our staff to be
OL,14,Fsubject to violence and acts of
OL,15,Fvandalism whilst protecting the public.
