OL,6,F"Our job is being made more difficult
OL,7,Fby the thoughtless actions of a
OL,8,Fminority intent on setting fires and
OL,9,Fthen trying to injure staff and damage
OL,10,Fengines. In this instance it means a
OL,11,Fvehicle is off the road and
OL,12,Funavailable to respond to other
OL,13,Fincidents. These attacks also divert
OL,14,Fcrews from real emergencies where
OL,15,Flives may be at risk.
