OL,6,F"Such violence also puts firefighters
OL,7,Fat risk of serious injury. Cleveland
OL,8,FFire Brigade will not tolerate such
OL,9,Fattacks. Our vehicles are fitted with
OL,10,FCCTV cameras and staff are equipped
OL,11,Fwith body cams and we will use any
OL,12,Fevidence we have to support the police
OL,13,Fto secure a prosecution of anyone who
OL,14,Fhas been violent towards our staff and
OL,15,Fvandalised property."
OL,17,FAnyone who can help identify those
OL,18,Fresponsible for the damage is asked to
OL,19,Fcontact Firestoppers anonymously via
OL,20,Ftheir , or by phone on 0800 169 5558.
